      "text": "# рҹҡҖ Automated Trading Platform вҖ” Complete Architecture\n**Stack:** FastAPI (Python 3.11) В· React 18 + TypeScript В· SQLite В· Docker В· Angel One Broker\n**Markets:** NSE / BSE / MCX India &nbsp;|&nbsp; **Modes:** BACKTEST вҶ’ PAPER вҶ’ SHADOW_LIVE вҶ’ LIVE_AUTO_LIMITED вҶ’ LIVE",
