    {
      "id": "e2e_flow",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## вҡЎ End-to-End Data Flow\n\n```\n[Browser :3100] в”Җв”ҖHTTPSв”Җв”Җв–ә [Nginx Proxy] в”Җв”Җв–ә [FastAPI :8000] в”Җв”Җв–ә [TradingRuntime]\n      в”Ӯ                                             в”Ӯ                      в”Ӯ\n      в”Ӯв—„в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ WebSocket /ws/dashboard push в—„в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ              [Agent Loop]\n      в”Ӯ                (every 5s)                                  every 300s\n [Zustand Store]                                         [Decision Pipeline]\n   (19 views)                               regime вҶ’ strategy вҶ’ signal вҶ’ risk вҶ’ order\n                                                               в”Ӯ\n                                                    [Execution Router]\n                                              paper / backtest / live broker\n                                                               в”Ӯ\n                                              [Angel One API]  [SQLite DB]\n```\n\n**Auth:** Bearer token on all mutating endpoints В· WebSocket auth via payload\n**Ports:** Frontend 3100 вҶ’ 3000 В· API 8100 вҶ’ 8000 (Docker mapped)",
      "x": -1400,
      "y": -3510,
