    },
    {
      "id": "fe_views",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## рҹ“„ Views (19 Pages)\n\n| View | Path | Purpose |\n|------|------|---------|\n| **Dashboard** | `/` | Real-time P&L, positions, agent status, WS feed |\n| **Engine** | `/engine` | Scheduler stats, rate limiter, OMS events |\n| **Signals** | `/signals` | Signal scan trigger, candidate table, regime |\n| **Strategies** | `/strategies` | Strategy catalog, evaluation leaderboard |\n| **Backtest** | `/backtest` | Backtest runner, walk-forward validation |\n| **Models** | `/models` | Volatility forecast, regime classify, meta-rank |\n| **Risk** | `/risk` | Risk rejections, compliance, event-risk guard |\n| **Execution** | `/execution` | Order queue, manual approvals, multi-leg orders |\n| **Account** | `/account` | Positions, cash, equity, target progress |\n| **AI Council** | `/ai-council` | Agent votes, debate, risk critic, proposals |\n| **Neural Lab** | `/neural` | Forecast bundle, tail risk, correlation, charts |\n| **Quantum Lab** | `/quantum` | Portfolio optimization, backend status |\n| **MARL Lab** | `/marl` | Multi-agent RL advisory preview |\n| **Goal Governor** | `/goal` | Annual profit target tracking, scaling |\n| **Policies** | `/policies` | RL policy registry, promote/rollback |\n| **Intelligence** | `/intelligence` | News sentiment, economic calendar, regime |\n| **Trace Replay** | `/traces` | Decision trace store, timeline replay |\n| **Tournament** | `/tournament` | Strategy tournament validation |\n| **AI Lab** | `/ai-lab` | High-end scan: Council + Neural + Quantum |",
      "x": -4100,
      "y": -2980,
      "width": 1500,
      "height": 700,
