    },
    {
      "id": "fe_state",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## рҹ—ғпёҸ Zustand Store (store.ts)\n\n**Navigation**\n- `activeView: NavView`\n\n**Live WS State**\n- `runtimeState: RuntimeState`\n- `monitoring: MonitoringMetrics`\n- `liveFeed: LiveFeedSnapshot`\n- `dbSummary: DBSummary`\n- `livePortfolio: LivePortfolioSnapshot`\n- `applyWsSnapshot()` вҖ” merges snapshot\n\n**Analytics**\n- `equityCurve`, `dailyPnl`, `recentTrades`\n- `targetProgress`\n\n**AI Labs**\n- `aiCouncilStatus`, `aiCouncilDecisions[]`\n- `neuralStatus`, `latestNeuralBundle`\n- `quantumStatus`, `latestQuantumResult`\n- `goalGovernorStatus`\n- `latestHighEndScan`\n\n**Other**\n- `signalResult`, `strategyResult`\n- `backtestResult`, `walkForwardResult`\n- `modelCatalog[]`, `policies[]`\n- `recentTraces[]`\n- `loading: LoadingState`\n- `error: string | null`",
      "x": -4100,
      "y": -2210,
      "width": 720,
      "height": 660,
      "color": "4"
    },
    {
      "id": "fe_apiclient",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## рҹ”Ң API Client (api.ts + ws.ts)\n\n**HTTP Client** (api.ts)\n- Base URL: `http://localhost:8100`\n- Auth header: `Authorization: Bearer <token>`\n- `get<T>(path)` / `post<T>(path, body)`\n\n**Key API Functions**\n```typescript\ngetHealth()           вҶ’ HealthResponse\ngetRuntimeState()     вҶ’ RuntimeState\nrunSignalScan()       вҶ’ SignalScanResult\nrunStrategyEval()     вҶ’ StrategyEvaluationResult\nrunBacktest()         вҶ’ BacktestResult\nrunHighEndScan()      вҶ’ HighEndScanResult\ngetAICouncilStatus()  вҶ’ AICouncilStatus\nrunAICouncilPreview() вҶ’ AICouncilDecision\nrunNeuralPreview()    вҶ’ NeuralBundle\nrunQuantumPreview()   вҶ’ QuantumOptimizationResult\nrunMarlAdvisory()     вҶ’ MarlAdvisoryResult\ngetGoalGovernor()     вҶ’ GoalGovernorStatus\nlistTraces()          вҶ’ { traces[] }\ngetTraceReplay()      вҶ’ TraceReplayResponse\nlistPolicies()        вҶ’ { policies[] }\npromotePolicy()       вҶ’ void\n```\n\n**WebSocket** (ws.ts)\n- `ws://localhost:8100/ws/dashboard`\n- Auth via first message payload\n- Pushes `WsDashboardMessage` every 5s\n- Reconnect with exponential backoff",
      "x": -3330,
      "y": -2210,
      "width": 730,
      "height": 660,
      "color": "4"
    },
    {
      "id": "fe_components",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## рҹ§© Shared Components\n\n**Layout**\n- `Layout.tsx` вҖ” Sidebar + header wrapper\n- `Header.tsx` вҖ” WS status, mode badge, kill switch\n- `Sidebar.tsx` вҖ” 19-view navigation\n\n**Shared UI** (`components/shared/`)\n- `Card` / `CardHeader` / `CardBody`\n- `Table<T>` вҖ” typed columns (label, render, align)\n- `Badge` / `Tag` вҖ” colored status chips\n- `StatTile` вҖ” metric tile (value, accent, sub)\n- `KeyValueGrid` вҖ” labeled k/v pairs\n- `ProgressBar` вҖ” linear progress with accent\n- `JsonPanel` вҖ” syntax-highlighted JSON\n- `PageHeader` вҖ” title + subtitle + action slot\n\n**Types** (types.ts)\n- 45+ TypeScript interfaces\n- All use `[key: string]: unknown` index sig\n- Covers: Agent, Neural, Quantum, MARL, Risk,\n  Portfolio, Broker, Events, Policies, Traces",
      "x": -4100,
