    {
      "id": "api_header",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## рҹҢҗ API GATEWAY вҖ” FastAPI (trading_platform/api/app.py) вҖ” 118 Endpoints",
      "x": -2490,
      "y": -3100,
      "width": 1200,
      "height": 60,
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "api_public",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## рҹ”“ Public Endpoints (No Auth)\n\n```\nGET  /health              вҶ’ liveness probe\nGET  /state               вҶ’ RuntimeState snapshot\nGET  /live/readiness      вҶ’ 7-gate checklist\nGET  /universe            вҶ’ tradeable instruments\nGET  /strategies/catalog  вҶ’ strategy list\nGET  /models/catalog      вҶ’ model list\nGET  /monitoring/metrics  вҶ’ real-time metrics\nGET  /monitoring/events   вҶ’ event stream\nGET  /governance          вҶ’ governance dashboard\nGET  /account/status      вҶ’ broker profile/funds\nGET  /feed/snapshot       вҶ’ latest tick prices\nGET  /feed/tick/{symbol}  вҶ’ single symbol tick\nGET  /regime/current      вҶ’ market regime\nGET  /ai-council/status   вҶ’ AI council health\nGET  /quantum/status      вҶ’ quantum kernel\nGET  /neural/status       вҶ’ neural service\nGET  /goal-governor/statusвҶ’ goal tracking\nGET  /derivatives/expiries/{u}    вҶ’ expiry dates\nGET  /derivatives/option-chain/{u}вҶ’ Greeks/chain\nWS   /ws/dashboard        вҶ’ real-time push\n```",
      "x": -2490,
      "y": -2980,
      "width": 1200,
      "height": 540,
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "api_auth",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## рҹ”җ Authenticated Endpoints (Bearer Token)\n\n**Control**\n```\nPOST /live/arm              вҶ’ arm/disarm live\nPOST /execution-mode        вҶ’ switch mode\nPOST /kill-switch           вҶ’ emergency halt\nPOST /agent/start|stop      вҶ’ agent lifecycle\nPOST /agent/interval        вҶ’ set scan interval\n```\n**Trading**\n```\nPOST /signals/scan          вҶ’ scan signals\nPOST /strategies/evaluate   вҶ’ run evaluation\nPOST /backtests/run         вҶ’ run backtest\nPOST /backtests/walk-forwardвҶ’ walk-forward\nPOST /orders/paper          вҶ’ simulate order\nPOST /execution/enqueue     вҶ’ enqueue order\nPOST /execution/multi-leg   вҶ’ complex options\nPOST /execution/square-off  вҶ’ close all\n```\n**AI/ML**\n```\nPOST /high-end/scan         вҶ’ full AI scan\nPOST /ai-council/preview    вҶ’ council advisory\nPOST /neural/predict-previewвҶ’ neural bundle\nPOST /quantum/optimize-preview вҶ’ portfolio opt\nPOST /marl/advisory-preview вҶ’ MARL advisory\nGET  /ai-council/decisions  вҶ’ history\nGET  /quantum/results       вҶ’ opt results\nGET  /neural/meta-labeler   вҶ’ labeler status\nGET  /paper/learning-journalвҶ’ learning events\n```\n**Data & DB**\n```\nPOST /data/instruments/refresh вҶ’ master fetch\nPOST /data/candles          вҶ’ OHLCV history\nGET  /db/trades|equity-curve|daily-pnl\nGET  /portfolio/positions\nGET  /risk/rejections|compliance\nGET  /traces                вҶ’ decision traces\nGET  /traces/{id}/replay    вҶ’ trace replay\nGET  /policies              вҶ’ RL policies\nPOST /policies/promote|rollback\n```",
      "x": -2490,
      "y": -2380,
      "width": 1200,
      "height": 820,
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "api_auth_layer",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## рҹ”‘ Auth Middleware\n\n```python\n# trading_platform/api/app.py\nasync def verify_token(credentials):\n    if not settings.api_auth_required:\n        return  # CI / dev bypass\n    if credentials.credentials != settings.api_auth_token:\n        raise HTTPException(401)\n```\n\n**Config flags**\n- `API_AUTH_REQUIRED=false` (dev/CI)\n- `API_AUTH_TOKEN=<secret>` (prod)\n- CORS: localhost:3100, localhost:5173",
      "x": -2490,
      "y": -1500,
      "width": 580,
      "height": 350,
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "api_runtime",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## вҡҷпёҸ TradingRuntime (api/runtime.py)\n\nSingleton orchestrator holding all services:\n\n```python\nclass TradingRuntime:\n    settings: Settings\n    broker: BrokerAdapter          # paper/live\n    persistence: PersistenceLayer  # SQLite\n    risk_engine: RiskEngine\n    execution_router: ExecutionRouter\n    oms: OrderManagementSystem\n    portfolio: PortfolioLedger\n    event_bus: EventBus\n    live_feed: LiveFeedService\n    neural_service: NeuralServingService\n    quantum_service: QuantumService\n    ai_council: AICouncilService\n    marl_service: MARLService\n    goal_governor: GoalGovernorService\n    trace_store: TraceStore\n    policy_registry: PolicyRegistry\n```\n\n**Lifecycle**\n1. `startup()` вҶ’ init all services\n2. Optionally auto-start agent & live feed\n3. `shutdown()` вҶ’ graceful close",
      "x": -1860,
      "y": -1500,
      "width": 570,
      "height": 480,
      "color": "5"
    },

    {
      "id": "backend_header",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## вҡҷпёҸ CORE BACKEND вҖ” Agent Loop В· Decision Pipeline В· Execution",
      "x": -1180,
      "y": -3100,
      "width": 1100,
      "height": 60,
      "color": "2"
    },
    {
      "id": "agent_loop",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## рҹӨ– Agent Loop (agent/trading_agent.py)\n\n**Cycle every 300s (configurable):**\n```\n1. market_hours.check() вҶ’ skip if closed\n2. live_feed.sync_prices() вҶ’ update marks\n3. exit_manager.check_exits() вҶ’ SL/TP triggers\n4. for underlying in SCAN_UNDERLYINGS:\n     decision_pipeline.scan(underlying)\n       вҶ’ DecisionCandidate[]\n     for candidate in approved:\n       execution_router.enqueue(candidate)\n5. publish AgentCycleResult вҶ’ event_bus\n```\n\n**Scheduled Events (IST)**\n- `09:00` Pre-market: refresh instruments, start feed\n- `09:15` Market open: begin scan loop\n- `15:25` EOD: square-off all open positions\n- `15:30` Market close: stop feed, publish EOD report\n\n**MCX Extended:** continues until 23:30 for commodities",
      "x": -1180,
      "y": -2980,
      "width": 1100,
      "height": 420,
      "color": "2"
    },
    {
      "id": "decision_pipe",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## рҹ§  Decision Pipeline (decision/pipeline.py)\n\n```\nDecisionPipeline.scan(underlying):\n  в”Ӯ\n  в”ңв”Җ 1. RegimeClassifier.classify()\n  в”Ӯ      вҶ’ BULLISH / BEARISH / VOLATILE /\n  в”Ӯ        NEUTRAL / TRENDING / EVENT_RISK\n  в”Ӯ\n  в”ңв”Җ 2. StrategyFactory.select(regime)\n  в”Ӯ      вҶ’ equity: momentum, mean-reversion\n  в”Ӯ        derivatives: covered_call, iron_condor\n  в”Ӯ        synthetic: pairs, spread\n  в”Ӯ\n  в”ңв”Җ 3. Signal.compute(bars, features)\n  в”Ӯ      вҶ’ side: BUY/SELL, confidence, price\n  в”Ӯ\n  в”ңв”Җ 4. PositionSizer.compute()\n  в”Ӯ      вҶ’ regime-aware + target-scaled qty\n  в”Ӯ\n  в”ңв”Җ 5. RiskEngine.evaluate(candidate)\n  в”Ӯ      вҶ’ approved: bool, risk_score, reason\n  в”Ӯ\n  в””в”Җ 6. DecisionTrace.record()\n         вҶ’ SQLite trace_store\n```\n\n**Decision Fusion** (decision_fusion/)\n- Ensemble: merge AI Council + Neural + Quantum\n- GoalGovernor: scale positions per profit target",
      "x": -1180,
      "y": -2500,
      "width": 1100,
      "height": 560,
      "color": "2"
    },
    {
      "id": "exec_layer",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## рҹ“Ӣ Execution Layer (execution/)\n\n**Components:**\n- `OrderManagementSystem` вҖ” order lifecycle events\n- `ExecutionRouter` вҖ” broker selection per mode\n- `ExecutionScheduler` вҖ” rate limiter (orders/min)\n- `FillProcessor` вҖ” slippage + charge calc\n- `MultiLegManager` вҖ” complex options strategies\n- `ManualApprovalGate` вҖ” human review for large orders\n- `ExitManager` вҖ” SL/TP/trailing-stop tracking\n- `ReconciliationService` вҖ” broker position sync\n- `EmergencySquareOff` вҖ” kill-switch close all\n\n**Order Flow:**\n```\nenqueue(OrderIntent)\n  вҶ’ validate (mode, symbol, qty, risk)\n  вҶ’ market_hours check\n  вҶ’ ManualApprovalGate (if notional > threshold)\n  вҶ’ ExecutionScheduler.rate_check()\n  вҶ’ broker.submit_order()\n  вҶ’ FillProcessor.apply(slippage, charges)\n  вҶ’ portfolio.update()\n  вҶ’ persist trade вҶ’ SQLite\n  вҶ’ event_bus.publish(ORDER_FILLED)\n  вҶ’ WebSocket push вҶ’ dashboard\n```",
      "x": -1180,
      "y": -1880,
      "width": 1100,
      "height": 540,
      "color": "2"
    },
    {
      "id": "risk_engine",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## рҹӣЎпёҸ Risk Engine (risk/)\n\n**Limits (configurable in config.py):**\n- `max_drawdown: 10%` of peak equity\n- `max_daily_loss: 2%` of capital\n- `max_position_pct: 5%` per symbol\n- `max_margin_utilization: 60%`\n- `max_orders_per_day: 50`\n- `block_naked_option_selling: True`\n\n**Risk Checks:**\n```\nRiskEngine.evaluate(candidate):\n  1. drawdown guard вҶ’ reject if breached\n  2. daily loss circuit breaker\n  3. position concentration check\n  4. margin utilization check\n  5. compliance.check() (SEBI rules)\n  6. event_risk.check() (earnings, RBI, budget)\n  7. return RiskDecision(approved, score, reason)\n```\n\n**Governance (7-gate live readiness):**\n1. Auth token configured\n2. Instruments loaded\n3. Angel One credentials set\n4. Risk health OK\n5. Kill switch NOT active\n6. Market data NOT stale\n7. Live confirmation phrase set",
      "x": -1180,
      "y": -1280,
      "width": 1100,
      "height": 520,
      "color": "2"
    },

    {
      "id": "aiml_header",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## рҹ§Ә AI / ML LAYER вҖ” Council В· Neural В· Quantum В· MARL В· Goal Governor",
      "x": 120,
      "y": -3100,
      "width": 1100,
      "height": 60,
      "color": "6"
    },
    {
      "id": "ai_council",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## рҹҸӣпёҸ AI Council (agents/specialists.py)\n\n**Architecture:** Local LLM multi-agent debate\n\n**Agents:**\n- `TrendFollowingAgent` вҖ” momentum signals\n- `MeanReversionAgent` вҖ” statistical reversion\n- `VolatilityAgent` вҖ” regime + IV analysis\n- `RiskCriticAgent` вҖ” veto authority\n- `CoordinatorAgent` вҖ” debate orchestration\n\n**Decision Flow:**\n```\n1. Each agent votes: action + confidence\n2. If consensus < 0.65 вҶ’ trigger debate\n3. RiskCritic evaluates вҶ’ veto if score > 0.8\n4. PortfolioAgent вҶ’ max_heat sizing\n5. ExecutionAgent вҶ’ order_type advice\n6. Return AICouncilDecision:\n   { action, consensus_score, votes[],\n     risk_critique, strategy_proposals[] }\n```\n\n**LLM Backends** (Model Gateway):\n- `stub` вҖ” deterministic fallback (no LLM)\n- `ollama` вҖ” local Ollama server\n- `llama_cpp` вҖ” llama.cpp HTTP server\n- `vllm` вҖ” vLLM OpenAI-compatible server",
      "x": 120,
      "y": -2980,
      "width": 1100,
      "height": 520,
      "color": "6"
    },
    {
      "id": "neural_lab",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## рҹ§¬ Neural Lab (neural/)\n\n**Models:**\n- `DirectionForecaster` вҖ” P(up) per symbol\n- `VolatilityForecaster` вҖ” GARCH + LSTM\n- `SentimentAnalyzer` вҖ” news/text scoring\n- `GraphCorrelationModel` вҖ” pairwise correlation\n- `TailRiskEstimator` вҖ” extreme move probability\n\n**NeuralBundle output:**\n```python\n{\n  should_trade: bool,       # uncertainty gate\n  overall_uncertainty: float,\n  forecasts: [\n    { symbol, direction_probability,\n      expected_return, model_uncertainty }\n  ],\n  tail_risks: [\n    { symbol, extreme_move_probability,\n      expected_max_drawdown }\n  ],\n  correlation_risk: {\n    max_pairwise_correlation,\n    contagion_risk_score\n  }\n}\n```\n\n**Meta-Labeler:**\n- Labels decisions with outcomes post-trade\n- Feeds learning journal for RL training\n- Updates meta-model weights online",
      "x": 120,
      "y": -2400,
      "width": 1100,
      "height": 540,
      "color": "6"
    },
    {
      "id": "quantum_lab",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## вҡӣпёҸ Quantum Lab (quantum/)\n\n**Purpose:** Portfolio subset selection via QUBO\n\n**Backends:**\n- `classical` вҖ” brute-force / greedy solver\n- `qiskit` вҖ” QAOA / VQE simulation\n- `dwave` вҖ” D-Wave Leap annealing (cloud)\n\n**QUBO Formulation:**\n```\nminimize: -ОЈ edge_iВ·x_i + О»В·ОЈ_ij corr_ijВ·x_iВ·x_j\nsubject to: ОЈ x_i = K  (cardinality gate)\n            x_i вҲҲ {0,1}\n```\n\n**Output: QuantumOptimizationResult**\n```python\n{\n  selected_symbols: str[],\n  backend_used: str,\n  objective_value: float,\n  classical_baseline_objective: float,\n  improvement_over_classical: float,\n  beats_baseline: bool,\n  constraints_satisfied: bool\n}\n```\n\n**Gate:** Only use if `improvement > min_threshold`",
      "x": 120,
      "y": -1800,
      "width": 1100,
      "height": 520,
      "color": "6"
    },
    {
      "id": "marl_lab",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## рҹӨқ MARL Lab (rl/ + agents/)\n\n**Multi-Agent Reinforcement Learning**\n\n**Agents:** Independent Q-learners per strategy\n**Environment:** Market simulation (rl/env.py)\n- State: OHLCV + technical features\n- Action: BUY / SELL / HOLD\n- Reward: risk-adjusted P&L\n\n**Policy Registry (policies/):**\n```\nresearch вҶ’ shadow вҶ’ paper вҶ’ live_canary\n         вҶ’ live_approved вҶ’ disabled\n```\nPromote via `/policies/promote`\nRollback via `/policies/rollback`\n\n**Advisory output:**\n```python\nMarlAdvisoryResult {\n  action: str, confidence: float,\n  majority_action_label: str,\n  majority_confidence: float\n}\n```",
      "x": 120,
      "y": -1220,
      "width": 1100,
      "height": 440,
      "color": "6"
    },
    {
      "id": "goal_governor",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## рҹҺҜ Goal Governor (goal/ + decision_fusion/)\n\n**Annual Target:** вӮ№5 crore (configurable)\n\n**Tracks:**\n- `realized_pnl` vs `required_daily_run_rate`\n- `current_equity`, `days_elapsed`\n- `drawdown_budget_remaining`\n\n**Scaling Logic:**\n- Ahead of target вҶ’ reduce position size\n- Behind target вҶ’ increase sizing (capped)\n- At max drawdown вҶ’ enter preservation mode\n\n**Output:**\n```python\nGoalGovernorStatus {\n  on_track: bool,\n  recommendation: str,  # SCALE_UP / MAINTAIN / REDUCE\n  allocation_bias: str,\n  max_scaling_multiplier: float\n}\n```",
      "x": 120,
      "y": -720,
      "width": 1100,
      "height": 380,
      "color": "6"
    },

    {
      "id": "strategies_header",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## рҹ“Ҳ STRATEGIES & BACKTESTING",
      "x": 1380,
      "y": -3100,
      "width": 960,
      "height": 60,
      "color": "3"
    },
    {
      "id": "strategies",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## рҹ“Ҡ Strategy Catalog (strategies/)\n\n**Equity Strategies:**\n- `MomentumStrategy` вҖ” 20-day breakout\n- `MeanReversionStrategy` вҖ” Bollinger bands\n- `TrendFollowingStrategy` вҖ” EMA crossover\n\n**Derivatives Strategies:**\n- `CoveredCallStrategy` вҖ” yield enhancement\n- `IronCondorStrategy` вҖ” range-bound premium\n- `BullCallSpreadStrategy` вҖ” directional options\n- `BearPutSpreadStrategy` вҖ” directional puts\n- `StrangleStrategy` вҖ” volatility play\n\n**Selection:**\n- Regime-based: BULLISHвҶ’momentum, VOLATILEвҶ’condor\n- Meta-model ranks strategies by recent performance\n- Walk-forward validation gates promotion\n\n**Options Engine (derivatives/):**\n- Greeks: Delta, Gamma, Theta, Vega, Rho\n- IV surface builder (Newton-Raphson)\n- Expiry calendar (weekly/monthly NSE)\n- Multi-leg order builder + rollover planner",
      "x": 1380,
      "y": -2980,
      "width": 960,
      "height": 620,
      "color": "3"
    },
    {
      "id": "backtesting",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## рҹ”Ғ Backtesting Engine (backtesting/)\n\n**Deterministic simulation (no lookahead):**\n```\nfor each bar t in [start, end]:\n  signal = strategy.compute(bars[0:t-1])\n  if signal and risk.approve():\n    exec at bar[t].open\n    slippage = bid_ask_halfspread\n               + sqrt_impact * sqrt(qty/ADV)\n    charges = brokerage + STT + stamp\n            + SEBI + exchange_fee\n    portfolio.fill(price + slippage + charges)\n\nmetrics:\n  Sharpe-like ratio, max_drawdown,\n  win_rate, profit_factor, return_pct\n```\n\n**Walk-Forward Validation:**\n- Train window вҶ’ test window (rolling)\n- Degradation detection: test_sharpe < train*0.7\n- `mean_test_return`, `mean_test_sharpe`\n\n**Charges (Indian Markets):**\n- Brokerage: 0.03% / вӮ№20 cap\n- STT: 0.1% on equity delivery\n- Exchange: 0.00345% NSE\n- SEBI: вӮ№10 per crore\n- GST: 18% on brokerage",
      "x": 1380,
      "y": -2300,
      "width": 960,
      "height": 620,
      "color": "3"
    },
    {
      "id": "portfolio",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## рҹ’° Portfolio & Analytics\n\n**Portfolio Ledger (portfolio/ledger.py):**\n- Cash / equity / realized P&L / unrealized P&L\n- Peak equity / drawdown tracking\n- Open positions with FIFO cost basis\n- Position scaling via GoalGovernor\n\n**Performance Metrics:**\n```python\nPortfolioSnapshot {\n  cash, equity, realized_pnl,\n  unrealized_pnl, drawdown, peak_equity\n}\n\nTargetProgress {\n  annual_target, start_capital,\n  current_equity, realized_pnl,\n  elapsed_days, required_run_rate,\n  current_gap, allocation_bias\n}\n```\n\n**Validation (validation/):**\n- `MonteCarloValidator` вҖ” 1000 path simulation\n- `TournamentEvaluator` вҖ” strategy head-to-head\n- `PostMortemAnalyzer` вҖ” trade attribution",
      "x": 1380,
      "y": -1620,
      "width": 960,
      "height": 500,
      "color": "3"
    },

    {
      "id": "data_header",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## рҹ“Ў DATA LAYER вҖ” Angel One В· Live Feed В· Instruments В· Synthetic",
      "x": -4100,
      "y": -880,
      "width": 2300,
      "height": 60,
      "color": "2"
    },
    {
      "id": "broker_adapter",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## рҹҸҰ Broker Adapters (broker/)\n\n**Angel One (Live)**\n```python\nAngelOneBroker:\n  login()          вҶ’ TOTP auth\n  get_profile()    вҶ’ account info\n  get_funds()      вҶ’ margin/cash\n  place_order()    вҶ’ NSE/BSE order\n  get_positions()  вҶ’ open positions\n  get_holdings()   вҶ’ delivery holdings\n  cancel_order()   вҶ’ order cancel\n```\n- SmartAPI REST client\n- TOTP-based session refresh\n- Rate limiting: 3 req/sec\n\n**SimulatedBroker (Paper/Backtest)**\n- In-memory order book\n- Market order fill at last tick\n- Slippage + charges applied\n- No external API calls\n\n**Capability Registry:**\n- Runtime broker feature detection\n- Graceful fallback to simulated",
      "x": -4100,
      "y": -760,
      "width": 740,
      "height": 580,
      "color": "2"
    },
    {
      "id": "live_feed",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## рҹ“¶ Live Feed (data/live_feed.py)\n\n**Angel One WebSocket feed:**\n- Subscribe up to 80 symbols\n- Receives: LTP, volume, OI ticks\n- Updates in-memory tick store\n- Publishes TICK events вҶ’ event_bus\n\n**Symbols:**\n```python\ndefault = [\n  'NIFTY', 'BANKNIFTY', 'FINNIFTY',\n  'RELIANCE', 'TCS', 'INFY', 'HDFC',\n  'ICICIBANK', 'AXISBANK', 'SBIN', ...\n]\n```\n\n**Status:**\n```python\nLiveFeedSnapshot {\n  running: bool,\n  subscribed_symbols: str[],\n  tick_count: int\n}\n```\n\n**Historical Data:**\n- `angel_one_history.py` вҶ’ OHLCV candles\n- Timeframes: 1m, 5m, 15m, 1d\n- Cached to `data/` directory\n- Synthetic fallback for backtests",
      "x": -3300,
      "y": -760,
      "width": 740,
      "height": 580,
      "color": "2"
    },
    {
      "id": "instruments",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## рҹ“Ӣ Instrument Master (data/)\n\n**Angel One Instrument Cache:**\n- Downloads full NSE/BSE/MCX master\n- ~50k+ instruments (equity + F&O)\n- Cached to `data/instruments.json`\n- Refreshed daily at pre-market\n\n**Token Lookup:**\n```python\nInstrumentMaster.lookup(symbol)\n  вҶ’ { token, exchange, segment,\n      lot_size, tick_size, expiry }\n```\n\n**Universe (domain/models.py):**\n```python\nInstrument {\n  symbol: str\n  exchange: Exchange  # NSE/BSE/MCX\n  segment: Segment    # EQ/FO/CD/MCX\n  type: str          # EQ/CE/PE/FUT\n  lot_size: int\n  expiry: date | None\n}\n```\n\n**Feature Store (ai/feature_store.py):**\n- RSI, MACD, BB, ATR, OBV, VWAP\n- Normalised technical indicators\n- Symbol-keyed feature vectors\n- Persisted for meta-labeling",
      "x": -2500,
      "y": -760,
      "width": 740,
      "height": 580,
      "color": "2"
    },
    {
      "id": "event_bus",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## рҹҡҢ Event Bus (event_bus.py)\n\n**In-memory pub/sub backbone:**\n\n**Streams:**\n- `TICKS` вҖ” live price updates\n- `ORDERS` вҖ” order lifecycle events\n- `FILLS` вҖ” trade fills\n- `RISK` вҖ” risk decisions\n- `AGENT` вҖ” agent cycle results\n- `LABELS` вҖ” outcome labels\n- `LEARNING` вҖ” meta-model updates\n\n**Usage:**\n```python\nevent_bus.publish('ORDERS', payload)\nevent_bus.subscribe('FILLS', handler)\n```\n\n**Dashboard push:**\n- WS handler subscribes to all streams\n- Aggregates into `WsDashboardMessage`\n- Pushes to all connected browsers\n\n**EventBusSummary:**\n```python\n{ event_count, streams: dict,\n  latest_event, backend: 'memory' }\n```",
      "x": -1700,
      "y": -760,
      "width": 740,
      "height": 580,
      "color": "2"
    },
    {
      "id": "trace_store",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## рҹ”Қ Trace Store (trace/store.py)\n\n**DecisionTrace вҖ” per-scan record:**\n```python\nDecisionTrace {\n  trace_id: str          # UUID\n  execution_mode: str\n  created_at: datetime\n  symbol_universe: str[]\n  quantum_result_id: str?\n  order_intent_ids: str[]\n  risk_decisions: dict[]\n  neural_model_versions: dict\n}\n```\n\n**TraceReplay вҖ” joined view:**\n```python\nTraceReplayResponse {\n  trace_id, trace,\n  summary: { status, lifecycle_complete,\n    order_count, fill_count,\n    journal_event_count, slippage_count,\n    label_count, learning_update_count },\n  timeline: event[],    # chronological\n  risk_decisions: []\n}\n```\n\n**Learning Journal (paper mode):**\n- Links decisions to outcomes\n- Computes outcome labels (win/loss/neutral)\n- Feeds meta-labeler for online learning",
      "x": -900,
      "y": -760,
      "width": 740,
      "height": 580,
      "color": "2"
    },

    {
      "id": "db_header",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## рҹ—„пёҸ DATABASE вҖ” SQLite (data/trading.db)",
      "x": 120,
      "y": -880,
      "width": 1100,
      "height": 60,
      "color": "3"
    },
    {
      "id": "database",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## рҹ“Ҡ SQLite Schema (data/persistence.py)\n\n**7 Core Tables:**\n\n```sql\ntrades\n  trade_id, order_id, symbol, side,\n  quantity, price, charges, timestamp,\n  strategy_name, execution_mode, is_test\n\nportfolio_snapshots\n  recorded_at, cash, equity,\n  realized_pnl, unrealized_pnl,\n  drawdown, execution_mode\n\ndaily_pnl\n  trade_date, realized_pnl, unrealized_pnl,\n  total_trades, winning_trades, ending_equity\n\nmodel_runs\n  run_at, model_name, symbol,\n  regime, signal, confidence, metadata\n\nrisk_events\n  occurred_at, event_type, symbol,\n  reason, risk_score, approved\n\nopen_positions\n  symbol, quantity, entry_price,\n  current_price, unrealized_pnl, mode\n\nfeature_history\n  symbol, timestamp, feature_vector (JSON)\n```\n\n**Thread safety:** `threading.RLock`\n**Location:** `/app/data/trading.db` (Docker volume)\n**Backup:** Mounted volume persists across restarts",
      "x": 120,
      "y": -760,
      "width": 1100,
      "height": 620,
      "color": "3"
    },
    {
      "id": "config",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## вҡҷпёҸ Configuration (config.py)\n\n**70+ settings via env vars:**\n\n```python\n# Execution\nEXECUTION_MODE=PAPER          # BACKTEST|PAPER|LIVE\nBROKER=ANGEL_ONE\nINITIAL_CAPITAL=1000000       # вӮ№10 lakh\n\n# Risk Limits\nMAX_DRAWDOWN=0.10\nMAX_DAILY_LOSS=0.02\nMAX_POSITION_PCT=0.05\nMAX_MARGIN_UTILIZATION=0.60\nMAX_ORDERS_PER_DAY=50\n\n# Angel One Credentials\nANGEL_ONE_API_KEY=...\nANGEL_ONE_CLIENT_CODE=...\nANGEL_ONE_TOTP_SECRET=...\n\n# API Auth\nAPI_AUTH_REQUIRED=false        # true in prod\nAPI_AUTH_TOKEN=<secret>\n\n# Feature Flags\nENABLE_AI_COUNCIL=true\nENABLE_NEURAL_LAB=true\nENABLE_QUANTUM_LAB=true\nENABLE_MARL_LAB=true\nENABLE_GOAL_GOVERNOR=true\n\n# LLM Gateway\nLLM_GATEWAY_MODE=stub          # ollama|llama_cpp|vllm\nLLM_BASE_URL=http://localhost:11434\n\n# Quantum\nQUANTUM_BACKEND=classical      # qiskit|dwave\nQUANTUM_CARDINALITY_K=5\n\n# Goals\nYEARLY_PROFIT_TARGET=5000000  # вӮ№50 lakh\n```",
      "x": 1380,
