    },
    {
      "id": "docker",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## рҹҗі Docker Compose (3 Services)\n\n**trading-api** (FastAPI)\n```yaml\nimage: automated-trading-ml-project-trading-api\nports: 127.0.0.1:8100:8000\nvolumes:\n  - ./data:/app/data\n  - ./backtest_results:/app/backtest_results\n  - ./models:/app/models\nhealthcheck:\n  test: curl -f http://localhost:8000/health\n  interval: 30s\n  start_period: 60s\n```\n\n**trading-scheduler** (Daily jobs)\n```yaml\ncommand: python scripts/daily_scheduler.py\ndepends_on:\n  trading-api: { condition: service_healthy }\nhealthcheck: checks API connectivity\n```\n\n**trading-frontend** (Nginx + React)\n```yaml\nbuild: hft_frontend/\nports: 127.0.0.1:3100:3000\ndepends_on:\n  trading-api: { condition: service_healthy }\n# Nginx proxies /api вҶ’ trading-api:8000\n# and          /ws  вҶ’ trading-api:8000/ws\n```\n\n**Network:** `trading-network` bridge\n**Build:** `docker compose build`\n**Start:** `docker compose up -d`\n**Logs:** `docker compose logs -f trading-api`",
      "x": -4100,
      "y": 340,
      "width": 1100,
      "height": 680,
      "color": "1"
    },
    {
      "id": "ci_cd",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## рҹ”„ CI/CD (GitHub Actions)\n\n**Workflow:** `.github/workflows/ci.yml`\n\n**Triggers:** push to any branch\n\n**Test step env vars:**\n```yaml\nenv:\n  API_AUTH_REQUIRED: \"false\"\n  AUTO_START_AGENT: \"false\"\n  AUTO_START_LIVE_FEED: \"false\"\n  ENABLE_AI_COUNCIL: \"false\"\n  ENABLE_NEURAL_LAB: \"false\"\n  ENABLE_QUANTUM_LAB: \"false\"\n  ENABLE_MARL_LAB: \"false\"\n  ENABLE_GOAL_GOVERNOR: \"false\"\n```\n\n**Command:**\n```bash\npython -m unittest discover -s tests -v\n```\n\n**Docker build workflow:**\n- Triggers on push to `main`\n- Builds and pushes to GHCR\n- Image tags: `latest` + commit SHA\n\n**Branches:**\n- `develop` вҖ” active development\n- `main` вҖ” production / Docker build",
      "x": -2900,
      "y": 340,
      "width": 900,
      "height": 680,
      "color": "1"
    },
    {
      "id": "testing",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## рҹ§Ә Test Suite (tests/ вҖ” 45+ files)\n\n**Core Integration:**\n- `test_architecture_wiring.py` вҖ” all components compose\n- `test_runtime.py` вҖ” TradingRuntime init + endpoints\n- `test_phase1.py` вҖ” full pipeline: backtest вҶ’ agent вҶ’ trades\n- `test_config.py` вҖ” settings validation\n\n**Execution & Risk:**\n- `test_backtesting.py` В· `test_risk_engine.py`\n- `test_execution_router.py` В· `test_decision_pipeline.py`\n- `test_derivatives_engine.py` В· `test_strategy_catalog.py`\n\n**Broker & Data:**\n- `test_angel_one_broker.py` В· `test_angel_one_data.py`\n- `test_instrument_master.py` В· `test_decision_fusion.py`\n\n**AI/ML:**\n- `test_ai_agents.py` В· `test_ai_models.py`\n- `test_neural_lab.py` В· `test_neural_serving_v2.py`\n- `test_quantum_service.py` В· `test_quantum_qubo.py`\n- `test_rl_lab.py` В· `test_meta_labeler.py`\n- `test_local_model_gateway.py`\n\n**Advanced:**\n- `test_high_end_integration.py` вҖ” Council + Neural + Quantum\n- `test_agent_council.py` В· `test_trace_store.py`\n- `test_vector_memory.py` В· `test_streaming_topics.py`\n- `test_validator_*.py` вҖ” walk-forward, Monte Carlo, tournament\n- `test_label_factory.py` В· `test_monitoring.py`",
      "x": -1700,
      "y": 340,
      "width": 1200,
      "height": 680,
      "color": "1"
    },
    {
      "id": "news_intel",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## рҹ“° Intelligence Layer (news/ + ai/)\n\n**News Sentiment (news/):**\n- `SentimentAnalyzer` вҖ” VADER + neural model\n- `EconomicCalendar` вҖ” RBI, budget, earnings dates\n- `NewsIntelligence` вҖ” scrape + analyze\n- `EventRiskGuard` вҖ” blocks orders during high-risk events\n\n**Regime Detection (ai/agents.py):**\n```python\nRegimeClassifier.classify(symbol, bars):\n  features = [\n    volatility_regime,   # ATR zscore\n    trend_strength,      # ADX\n    momentum_score,      # ROC 20d\n    volume_anomaly,      # volume zscore\n    options_skew,        # put-call ratio\n  ]\n  вҶ’ BULLISH | BEARISH | VOLATILE |\n    NEUTRAL | TRENDING_UP | TRENDING_DOWN |\n    EVENT_RISK\n```\n\n**Vector Memory (agents/vector_memory.py):**\n- Semantic search over historical decisions\n- Embeddings stored in-memory (FAISS-style)\n- Used by AI Council for context retrieval",
      "x": -400,
      "y": 340,
      "width": 1000,
      "height": 680,
      "color": "1"
    },
    {
      "id": "logging_safety",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## рҹ”’ Security & Logging\n\n**logging_safety.py:**\n- Redacts API keys, TOTPs, tokens from logs\n- Pattern-based secret scrubbing\n- Safe for production log aggregation\n\n**Execution Modes (domain/enums.py):**\n```python\nclass ExecMode(str, Enum):\n  BACKTEST = 'BACKTEST'\n  PAPER = 'PAPER'\n  SHADOW_LIVE = 'SHADOW_LIVE'\n  LIVE = 'LIVE'\n  LIVE_MANUAL_APPROVAL = 'LIVE_MANUAL_APPROVAL'\n  LIVE_AUTO_LIMITED = 'LIVE_AUTO_LIMITED'\n```\n\n**Kill Switch:**\n- `POST /kill-switch { reason: str }`\n- Immediately stops all new orders\n- Triggers emergency square-off\n- Requires manual re-arm to resume\n\n**Live Confirmation:**\n- Must set phrase: `I_ACCEPT_REAL_MONEY_LIVE_ORDERS`\n- Required before any live order executes\n- Separate from API auth token",
